        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Sunshine Protection Act of 2023</b></p> <p>This bill makes daylight saving time the new, permanent standard time.</p> <p>States with areas exempt from daylight saving time may choose the standard time for those areas.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
